'''Donique''' is a boy who visited the station with his father and brother.

==History==
In the wake of George Floyd's death, Donique and his brother, Corey, saw the video. Their father, wanting them to see first responders who looked like them, took them to station 19 and convinced Sullivan to show them around. They happily toured the station, wore some gear, and sat in the vehicles.

==Notes and Trivia==
*He is 11 years old and started sleeping with his comfort blanket again after seeing the George Floyd video.
